Numbeo Cost of Living Scraper
--------------------------------
This script scrapes cost of living data for a selected country from Numbeo
and exports it into an Excel file using pandas.

Steps:
1. Fetch main page and extract country links
2. Ask user for country name
3. Scrape cost-of-living table for that country
4. Save data as <country>.xlsx

Author: Dagarov Jokhongir
GitHub: https://github.com/Johongir2627/python_demo_projects/
